00:01:41,020 --> 00:01:43,940
=Episode 28=

3
00:01:44,260 --> 00:01:45,940
(Princess Fuhui's Mansion)

4
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:46,960
Lady Shen,

5
00:01:47,320 --> 00:01:48,880
the biluo you made

6
00:01:49,270 --> 00:01:50,710
is quite interesting.

7
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:52,730
Biluo originated
from the Western Regions

8
00:01:52,810 --> 00:01:55,010
and became very popular
after it was introduced here.

9
00:01:55,090 --> 00:01:56,160
My family and I

10
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:57,570
have developed several new flavors.

11
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:59,350
Using milk, eggs, and butter,

12
00:01:59,350 --> 00:02:00,520
we whip it into cream.

13
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:02,120
So, the ordinary cherry biluo

14
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,630
has become a cream cherry biluo.

15
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:06,120
This one that tastes like crab meat

16
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,760
is actually made from fish paste.

17
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:08,830
It's molded into shape

18
00:02:08,830 --> 00:02:10,150
to make a crab stick.

19
00:02:14,710 --> 00:02:16,150
From the Western Regions

20
00:02:16,150 --> 00:02:17,550
to the Central Plains.

21
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,990
We should let them see

22
00:02:19,990 --> 00:02:21,920
that after coming here,

23
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:24,480
the flavor has become more unique.

24
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:27,310
Actually, the idea of improving biluo

25
00:02:27,310 --> 00:02:28,430
was suggested by my father.

26
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:30,520
He said that a thousand years later,

27
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,640
people's hearts will change,

28
00:02:31,780 --> 00:02:33,960
and perhaps their tastes will change.

29
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,200
People might

30
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:36,830
forget this delicacy, biluo.

31
00:02:37,030 --> 00:02:38,800
But if we keep innovating,

32
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,030
maybe this dish

33
00:02:40,030 --> 00:02:41,360
can be passed down.

34
00:02:41,830 --> 00:02:42,800
Innovate?

35
00:02:43,710 --> 00:02:45,030
Create something new?

36
00:02:46,550 --> 00:02:47,830
What an interesting word.

37
00:02:48,650 --> 00:02:50,100
It seems that the reason your father

38
00:02:50,100 --> 00:02:52,600
can make Shen's Diner so successful

39
00:02:52,610 --> 00:02:55,270
is not only because he creates
new dishes

40
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:57,960
but also because his ideas are unique.

41
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,750
How can we eat biluo without tea?

42
00:03:07,030 --> 00:03:09,400
Today, I wanted to drink your tea,

43
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,240
so I had them

44
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,800
buy it for me.

45
00:03:15,150 --> 00:03:16,200
Your Highness, let me.

46
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,040
No need.

47
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:19,200
Today, I'll do it myself.

48
00:03:19,750 --> 00:03:20,590
Alright.

49
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:49,200
(Pei Fei)
Today,

50
00:03:49,200 --> 00:03:50,150
I ordered

51
00:03:50,150 --> 00:03:52,240
your Slap-the-Heartbreaker Drink.

52
00:03:56,870 --> 00:03:57,710
You always ignore me

53
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:58,890
and refuse my invitations.

54
00:03:58,890 --> 00:03:59,800
You always ignore me

55
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:00,900
and refuse my invitations.

56
00:04:05,780 --> 00:04:06,940
(Pei Fei)

57
00:04:08,500 --> 00:04:09,340
(Pei Fei)

58
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:22,120
Mr. Lin was impeached

59
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:24,070
for overstepping his authority.

60
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,190
He's been suspended by my brother.

61
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,640
What?

62
00:04:31,100 --> 00:04:34,100
(Upright in Speech and Conduct)

63
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,520
Young Master.

64
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:45,660
Young Master,

65
00:04:45,660 --> 00:04:46,720
Mr. Meng is here.

66
00:04:49,190 --> 00:04:50,030
Mr. Meng.

67
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,680
I've come to see

68
00:04:53,990 --> 00:04:55,240
how you are.

69
00:04:57,870 --> 00:04:59,430
Still calm.

70
00:04:59,870 --> 00:05:00,750
Don't worry.

71
00:05:00,750 --> 00:05:02,390
I came from the backyard.

72
00:05:02,820 --> 00:05:03,800
No one saw me.

73
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,600
Anran, do you know,

74
00:05:12,870 --> 00:05:14,120
throughout history,

75
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:16,720
what happened to those

76
00:05:17,070 --> 00:05:18,750
who were demoted
and fell into the abyss?

77
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:19,950
Out of ten,

78
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,460
hardly one or two

79
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,500
were able to make a comeback.

80
00:05:25,510 --> 00:05:27,680
Anran, you're alone

81
00:05:28,310 --> 00:05:29,700
with no ties,

82
00:05:30,510 --> 00:05:32,310
so you dare to speak for the people

83
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:33,600
and not fear the powerful.

84
00:05:34,870 --> 00:05:36,630
But that's also why

85
00:05:36,630 --> 00:05:39,390
they dared to target you.

86
00:05:42,380 --> 00:05:44,310
You want to advise me

87
00:05:45,420 --> 00:05:46,760
to choose a good tree to perch on.

88
00:05:50,390 --> 00:05:54,310
It's just about forming a good alliance.

89
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:58,630
If you became my grandson-in-law,

90
00:05:59,390 --> 00:06:02,800
you would never be demoted again.

91
00:06:08,340 --> 00:06:11,580
(Capital Prefecture)

92
00:06:25,310 --> 00:06:26,150
Go back.

93
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,560
All of you, go.

94
00:06:28,950 --> 00:06:30,040
It's not time to leave work.

95
00:06:30,310 --> 00:06:31,640
Yet, you all came to see me off.

96
00:06:32,190 --> 00:06:33,720
Do you think there's too little work?

97
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:37,960
In recent years,

98
00:06:38,790 --> 00:06:39,840
the head of the Prefecture

99
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:40,900
has changed too frequently.

100
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:43,050
It's not good for your promotions.

101
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:46,240
If I can't get through this time...

102
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,080
Mr. Lin,

103
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,600
at a time like this,

104
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,550
stop thinking about us.

105
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:51,040
If I can't get through this,

106
00:06:51,510 --> 00:06:52,510
I'll try to help you

107
00:06:53,070 --> 00:06:54,290
get transferred somewhere else.

108
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:56,880
Cheng Hu,

109
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:58,220
you'll go to the county

110
00:06:58,310 --> 00:06:59,750
and serve as the Sheriff for a while.

111
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:00,880
The salary will be higher,

112
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:03,170
and it will add to your resume.

113
00:07:04,510 --> 00:07:05,430
Second Master Xu,

114
00:07:05,430 --> 00:07:07,270
I'll recommend you
to the Ministry of Justice.

115
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:09,600
So you can hold your head high at home.

116
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:10,960
Zhao Jiu...

117
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,080
Mr. Lin.

118
00:07:12,550 --> 00:07:13,390
Stop.

119
00:07:13,450 --> 00:07:14,830
- We'll follow you.
- We'll stay.

120
00:07:14,900 --> 00:07:16,340
- Mr. Lin.
- We want to follow you.

121
00:07:16,340 --> 00:07:17,490
We just want to follow you.

122
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:21,840
But I can't see you

123
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:22,720
waste your time here.

124
00:07:22,870 --> 00:07:24,360
We aren't wasting our time.

125
00:07:25,190 --> 00:07:26,030
Mr. Lin.

126
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,990
With a Vice Prefect like you,

127
00:07:28,390 --> 00:07:29,800
we've never been afraid.

128
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:32,120
No matter what happens,

129
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,800
we will stick with you

130
00:07:34,500 --> 00:07:35,780
through thick and thin.

131
00:07:35,790 --> 00:07:37,240
- Right.
- Right.

132
00:07:42,660 --> 00:07:45,500
(Capital Prefecture)

133
00:07:51,580 --> 00:07:55,980
(Yunshui Manor)

134
00:08:01,990 --> 00:08:02,830
Young Master.

135
00:08:03,070 --> 00:08:04,390
Lady Shen is here.

136
00:08:14,660 --> 00:08:16,220
(Yunshui Manor)

137
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:19,660
Father and I made

138
00:08:19,660 --> 00:08:21,480
(Yunshui Manor)
several new flavors of biluo,

139
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,930
preparing to sell them in the diner.

140
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,750
Please have a try.

141
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,000
You already know?

142
00:08:37,560 --> 00:08:38,990
Your sudden suspension

143
00:08:39,760 --> 00:08:41,200
must be related to the case, right?

144
00:08:41,910 --> 00:08:43,360
Did Prince Zhao do this?

145
00:08:44,750 --> 00:08:45,590
Does your family

146
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:46,960
also know about it?

147
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:50,270
I received the news from the Princess.

148
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,080
I haven't told my family

149
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,120
so as not to worry them.

150
00:08:53,990 --> 00:08:55,220
Mr. Lin, don't be discouraged.

151
00:08:55,310 --> 00:08:56,560
Think of it from another angle.

152
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:57,750
It might be a good thing.

153
00:08:57,780 --> 00:08:58,960
The fact that they took action

154
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,090
as soon as you made progress

155
00:09:00,270 --> 00:09:01,720
only proves that you're right.

156
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,030
I'm fine, actually.

157
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:06,870
But you and I are cousins.

158
00:09:06,870 --> 00:09:08,420
Everyone in Yong'an has known about it.

159
00:09:08,870 --> 00:09:09,960
My suspension

160
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,670
will inevitably affect you.

161
00:09:12,270 --> 00:09:13,240
You've also helped a lot

162
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,390
with the case.

163
00:09:15,150 --> 00:09:15,990
From now on,

164
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:18,120
focus on protecting yourselves.

165
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:20,910
When family is in trouble,

166
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:23,200
that's the last thing we'd do.

167
00:09:28,170 --> 00:09:29,320
Mr. Lin, I came today

168
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:30,760
because I have something to tell you.

169
00:09:31,510 --> 00:09:33,870
The trap that Lu Yun set for you
at Yunlai Tavern

170
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:35,670
happened because someone
leaked the info.

171
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,960
Our newly hired chef, Yu San,

172
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,360
works for Prince Zhao.

173
00:09:40,510 --> 00:09:41,350
Yu San?

174
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,080
Where is he?

175
00:09:44,510 --> 00:09:45,720
Are your family members okay?

176
00:09:47,900 --> 00:09:49,750
Yu San is not a villain.

177
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,600
He was coerced by Prince Zhao.

178
00:09:51,770 --> 00:09:54,150
Prince Zhao held his parents hostage
in Fenglin Town,

179
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:56,360
so he had to agree
to work for Prince Zhao.

180
00:09:56,630 --> 00:09:59,150
If we can rescue his parents,

181
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:00,750
he's willing to help us.

182
00:10:02,790 --> 00:10:03,910
Fenglin Town?

183
00:10:05,390 --> 00:10:06,510
Can we

184
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:07,840
really trust Yu San?

185
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:10,080
After years of doing business,

186
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:11,960
I've developed a good eye for people.

187
00:10:12,990 --> 00:10:14,150
I think we can.

188
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:15,320
But it concerns...

189
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,160
I trust you.

190
00:10:21,710 --> 00:10:23,150
Leave the rest to me.

191
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:24,910
I'll head to Fenglin Town asap.

192
00:10:29,220 --> 00:10:31,380
(Yunshui Manor)

193
00:10:32,170 --> 00:10:33,240
It's raining hard.

194
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:35,120
Please get into the carriage quickly.

195
00:10:38,370 --> 00:10:40,130
Your sudden suspension

196
00:10:40,570 --> 00:10:41,960
must be related to the case, right?

197
00:10:42,230 --> 00:10:43,740
Did Prince Zhao do this?

198
00:10:48,910 --> 00:10:50,320
Sorry, I have to go back.

199
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,700
I forgot to tell Mr. Lin something.

200
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:54,080
Lady Shen, take the umbrella.

201
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:54,920
Thank you.

202
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,300
Don't come any closer.

203
00:11:26,860 --> 00:11:27,700
Father...

204
00:11:28,780 --> 00:11:30,140
Didn't Father die?

205
00:11:30,380 --> 00:11:31,300
Did I...

206
00:11:32,060 --> 00:11:33,340
Did I reincarnate

207
00:11:33,900 --> 00:11:35,460
to see Father once more?

208
00:11:36,700 --> 00:11:38,540
I can see Father again.

209
00:11:39,700 --> 00:11:40,900
Father...

210
00:11:46,140 --> 00:11:48,820
I can see Father again.

211
00:11:54,140 --> 00:11:55,780
Father...

212
00:11:58,620 --> 00:11:59,740
From now on,

213
00:12:00,180 --> 00:12:01,820
you shall be my adopted son.

214
00:12:02,460 --> 00:12:04,740
You'll have one character as your name,

215
00:12:05,460 --> 00:12:06,300
like my sons:

216
00:12:07,380 --> 00:12:08,340
Yan.

217
00:12:08,340 --> 00:12:09,180
Yes.

218
00:12:29,220 --> 00:12:30,060
Good.

219
00:12:30,700 --> 00:12:32,540
Your swordsmanship is getting better.

220
00:12:34,380 --> 00:12:35,380
You asked the masters

221
00:12:35,380 --> 00:12:36,860
to teach me swordsmanship.

222
00:12:37,940 --> 00:12:39,260
I hope I haven't disappointed you.

223
00:12:39,620 --> 00:12:41,620
You will never disappoint me.

224
00:12:41,900 --> 00:12:42,740
Are you tired?

225
00:12:42,900 --> 00:12:43,740
Have a cup of tea.

226
00:12:48,140 --> 00:12:48,980
Here.

227
00:12:49,780 --> 00:12:50,820
Thank you, Your Highness.

228
00:12:57,140 --> 00:12:57,980
Anran,

229
00:12:58,340 --> 00:12:59,380
I've heard that you want

230
00:12:59,380 --> 00:13:01,340
to be transferred to Yong'an.

231
00:13:01,980 --> 00:13:02,940
I think

232
00:13:02,940 --> 00:13:04,100
that if I can make a name

233
00:13:04,100 --> 00:13:05,140
for myself in the Capital,

234
00:13:05,580 --> 00:13:07,160
it won't be a waste of your cultivation.

235
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:09,740
Very well.

236
00:13:12,180 --> 00:13:13,020
Anran,

237
00:13:13,020 --> 00:13:13,980
I gave you

238
00:13:13,980 --> 00:13:15,180
your courtesy name.

239
00:13:17,380 --> 00:13:18,220
Do you know

240
00:13:19,010 --> 00:13:20,480
what it means?

241
00:13:23,940 --> 00:13:26,260
You hope that I can live

242
00:13:26,340 --> 00:13:27,440
a peaceful and smooth life.

243
00:13:27,500 --> 00:13:28,700
Now in the Capital,

244
00:13:29,500 --> 00:13:31,020
the situation is full of uncertainties.

245
00:13:31,380 --> 00:13:32,340
How can you

246
00:13:32,340 --> 00:13:33,620
make me feel at ease?

247
00:13:34,580 --> 00:13:35,660
I've already lost

248
00:13:35,660 --> 00:13:37,980
my most beloved eldest son.

249
00:13:39,220 --> 00:13:40,580
I don't want to lose you, either.

250
00:14:32,470 --> 00:14:34,020
Prince Zhao raised you.

251
00:14:34,730 --> 00:14:37,010
He's like a father to you.

252
00:14:38,590 --> 00:14:40,100
You found the evidence

253
00:14:40,780 --> 00:14:42,380
and confirmed that he's the culprit.

254
00:14:44,860 --> 00:14:46,740
Then he managed to get you suspended.

255
00:14:48,100 --> 00:14:50,020
You've been too calm about all that.

256
00:14:50,860 --> 00:14:52,100
If you keep these things inside,

257
00:14:52,100 --> 00:14:53,880
it can make you sick.

258
00:14:55,300 --> 00:14:57,540
So, treat me as a tree hole

259
00:14:57,540 --> 00:14:58,500
and let it out.

260
00:15:11,860 --> 00:15:12,780
He was so concerned

261
00:15:14,740 --> 00:15:15,820
about my studies.

262
00:15:18,260 --> 00:15:19,700
Liu Chang and I escaped death,

263
00:15:20,890 --> 00:15:21,900
wandering outside.

264
00:15:23,590 --> 00:15:24,620
My health weakened.

265
00:15:27,140 --> 00:15:28,220
He was afraid I would die,

266
00:15:29,540 --> 00:15:31,340
so he hired famous masters

267
00:15:31,780 --> 00:15:33,680
to teach me martial arts
to strengthen my body.

268
00:15:35,020 --> 00:15:36,180
He seemed

269
00:15:37,150 --> 00:15:38,820
so upright and sincere,

270
00:15:39,460 --> 00:15:42,740
and he taught me
to be loyal to the state

271
00:15:44,260 --> 00:15:45,740
and uphold righteousness.

272
00:15:48,140 --> 00:15:48,980
I know

273
00:15:50,540 --> 00:15:51,900
the reason he treated me this way

274
00:15:51,900 --> 00:15:52,740
is because I resemble

275
00:15:54,020 --> 00:15:56,540
his deceased eldest son, Li Sheng.

276
00:15:59,780 --> 00:16:00,620
Sheng

277
00:16:01,500 --> 00:16:02,340
and Yan

278
00:16:05,940 --> 00:16:07,940
both mean brightness.

279
00:16:11,540 --> 00:16:14,140
Even the courtesy name Anran

280
00:16:16,420 --> 00:16:18,300
was prepared for Li Sheng.

281
00:16:22,180 --> 00:16:23,740
But I still appreciate him.

282
00:16:25,250 --> 00:16:27,370
He saved me from the flames

283
00:16:27,900 --> 00:16:29,260
and taught me when I was confused.

284
00:16:31,150 --> 00:16:33,080
But I never expected...

285
00:16:35,640 --> 00:16:36,980
I just couldn't imagine

286
00:16:38,060 --> 00:16:40,180
that he had my family's blood
on his hands

287
00:16:40,180 --> 00:16:42,380
and still pretended to be my family.

288
00:16:46,660 --> 00:16:47,740
17 years.

289
00:16:50,300 --> 00:16:51,980
It's been 17 years.

290
00:16:53,380 --> 00:16:55,260
He preached righteousness,

