Mr. Lin.

579
00:34:18,820 --> 00:34:19,660
Mentor Zhao.

580
00:34:20,020 --> 00:34:21,020
Are you alright?

581
00:34:22,220 --> 00:34:23,420
I'm fine for now.

582
00:34:23,620 --> 00:34:24,540
Do you know

583
00:34:24,540 --> 00:34:26,420
where they're holding
the other hostages?

584
00:34:26,620 --> 00:34:27,820
The guards said

585
00:34:28,220 --> 00:34:29,620
they're also in Fenglin Town.

586
00:34:30,940 --> 00:34:31,780
Come with me.

587
00:35:18,460 --> 00:35:20,700
You actually found your way here.

588
00:35:21,170 --> 00:35:22,630
Lu Yun, that fool,

589
00:35:22,640 --> 00:35:24,860
even told my father
you hadn't found anything.

590
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:27,160
It seems I know you better after all.

591
00:35:28,100 --> 00:35:28,940
Lin Yan,

592
00:35:29,230 --> 00:35:31,420
I've been waiting here all along

593
00:35:31,740 --> 00:35:32,780
for you.

594
00:35:34,020 --> 00:35:36,540
It's because you resemble
my eldest brother

595
00:35:36,540 --> 00:35:37,860
that Father spared your life,

596
00:35:37,860 --> 00:35:39,580
letting you live these extra years.

597
00:35:42,100 --> 00:35:43,820
Kill this man

598
00:35:43,820 --> 00:35:46,500
who should've gone

599
00:35:47,180 --> 00:35:49,140
to hell 17 years ago.

600
00:35:56,660 --> 00:35:57,500
Li Ang,

601
00:35:57,620 --> 00:35:59,460
why give so many orders?

602
00:36:01,100 --> 00:36:02,460
Who can hear the key point?

603
00:36:03,460 --> 00:36:05,580
I told you to kill him!

604
00:36:18,860 --> 00:36:19,700
Attack Zhao.

605
00:36:19,700 --> 00:36:20,820
He will surely defend.

606
00:36:42,860 --> 00:36:44,140
Stop it, all of you.

607
00:36:44,900 --> 00:36:46,140
Father watched you learn

608
00:36:46,140 --> 00:36:47,820
your swordsmanship.

609
00:36:48,380 --> 00:36:50,100
He never treated me like this.

610
00:36:51,180 --> 00:36:53,780
Today, I will personally disable you

611
00:36:54,440 --> 00:36:56,460
and bring you before Father,

612
00:36:56,460 --> 00:36:58,580
so he can see

613
00:36:58,580 --> 00:37:01,100
how useless you are.

614
00:37:01,820 --> 00:37:02,700
Scatter.

615
00:37:38,220 --> 00:37:39,060
Slow down.

616
00:37:45,020 --> 00:37:45,860
Mr. Lin,

617
00:37:47,290 --> 00:37:48,840
hold on a little longer,

618
00:37:48,850 --> 00:37:49,910
okay?

619
00:37:50,700 --> 00:37:51,540
Come on.

620
00:38:07,810 --> 00:38:08,730
Be careful.

621
00:38:10,420 --> 00:38:11,260
Someone's coming.

622
00:38:14,140 --> 00:38:14,980
- Lin Yan.
- That...

623
00:38:15,580 --> 00:38:16,420
Mr. Lin!

624
00:38:17,100 --> 00:38:17,940
Lin Yan!

625
00:38:26,860 --> 00:38:27,700
Lin Yan.

626
00:38:29,540 --> 00:38:30,460
Lin Yan.

627
00:38:30,460 --> 00:38:31,980
It's okay now; I'm here.

628
00:38:31,980 --> 00:38:32,820
It's okay.

629
00:38:33,220 --> 00:38:34,500
It's okay now; I'm here.

630
00:38:34,740 --> 00:38:36,340
Yu San's parents

631
00:38:37,780 --> 00:38:39,140
are being held

632
00:38:39,990 --> 00:38:42,260
somewhere else in Fenglin Town.

633
00:38:45,060 --> 00:38:46,580
Mentor Zhao knows.

634
00:38:47,580 --> 00:38:48,900
Let Cheng Hu

635
00:38:50,380 --> 00:38:53,180
take people to rescue them.

636
00:38:56,860 --> 00:38:58,060
Liu Chang will be here soon.

637
00:38:58,220 --> 00:38:59,500
Hold on a little longer.

638
00:38:59,740 --> 00:39:01,060
He's right behind us.

639
00:39:01,220 --> 00:39:02,580
Don't fall asleep. Hold on.

640
00:39:11,220 --> 00:39:14,900
(Shaoguang's Food Notes: Lemon Tea)

641
00:39:14,900 --> 00:39:20,100
(Why not join the Princess
to beat up the heartbreaker?)

642
00:39:20,100 --> 00:39:26,500
(The Slap-the-Heartbreaker Drink
is back.)

643
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:48,650
♪Wear a sunset glow upon the brow♪

644
00:39:48,650 --> 00:39:51,910
♪Breeze sways,
wind chimes hang below the cloud♪

645
00:39:52,230 --> 00:39:55,250
♪Hear one chime ring,
tugging at the heart♪

646
00:39:55,250 --> 00:39:58,350
♪True feelings perhaps
can only be sensed♪

647
00:39:58,930 --> 00:40:02,360
♪Misty is you, clear is you♪

648
00:40:02,360 --> 00:40:05,780
♪Seeking stars in fog,
seeing your shadow under the moon♪

649
00:40:05,780 --> 00:40:09,170
♪Words held back, feelings unrestrained♪

650
00:40:09,170 --> 00:40:14,320
♪Could the road ahead,
let us gaze but not doubt♪

651
00:40:16,280 --> 00:40:19,420
♪Mistook all eyes see as cold ice♪

652
00:40:19,420 --> 00:40:22,820
♪Yet let dusk dye
the ears and temples red♪

653
00:40:23,060 --> 00:40:26,120
♪Even holding breath
couldn't help but stop♪

654
00:40:26,120 --> 00:40:29,170
♪Exposing my warmed heart held tight♪

655
00:40:29,760 --> 00:40:33,220
♪Bustling is you, desolate is you♪

656
00:40:33,220 --> 00:40:36,600
♪Reservedly drawing you into this life♪

657
00:40:36,600 --> 00:40:40,030
♪Hesitating, undecided,
the heart hard to deceive♪

658
00:40:40,030 --> 00:40:45,850
♪Worldly rules and taboos,
how could they make me give up♪

659
00:40:46,090 --> 00:40:50,460
♪When rushing to you,
leaving my deep thoughts in disarray♪

660
00:40:50,460 --> 00:40:52,730
♪I still foolishly see it
as a good time♪

661
00:40:52,730 --> 00:40:57,050
♪Heart stirs,
wind swirls the lightest ripples♪

662
00:40:57,050 --> 00:40:59,820
♪A thousand tangled thoughts concealed♪

663
00:40:59,820 --> 00:41:04,100
♪Saved a whole lifetime,
hastening to you, urgent over miles♪

664
00:41:04,100 --> 00:41:07,540
♪To make the wandering heart
return home henceforth♪

665
00:41:07,540 --> 00:41:10,980
♪To draw near what seems beyond reach♪

666
00:41:10,980 --> 00:41:15,830
♪Through life and death changes,
only we never cease, never yield♪

667
00:41:15,830 --> 00:41:20,550
♪Perhaps affection barely passes muster♪

668
00:41:20,550 --> 00:41:22,720
♪But love forever♪

669
00:41:22,730 --> 00:41:28,490
♪Will make up for our mutual care,
mutual bond♪

670
00:41:28,770 --> 00:41:33,310
♪Saved a whole lifetime,
hastening to you, urgent over miles♪

671
00:41:33,310 --> 00:41:36,670
♪To make the wandering heart
return home from now♪

672
00:41:36,670 --> 00:41:40,140
♪To dare approach
what seems beyond reach♪

673
00:41:40,140 --> 00:41:41,880
♪Through life and death changes♪

674
00:41:41,880 --> 00:41:48,240
♪Only you, never cease, never yield♪
